{"tid":2089370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話我地係被選中既細路，咁佢地係點樣擊敗敵人嫁？","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T15:51:59.000Z","uid":65457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"046bbee82fb5a0d83e51c97c4bacb6e9d7230e3f","tid":2089370,"uid":65457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:34:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/hoairw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fhoairw&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9YPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=c517ed09\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/hoairw</a><br />\n<br />\n黎緊我地可能會面對更加多會令我地好驚、諗都冇諗過既事情發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間可能會更加長，甚至以十年計<br />\n但係又有邊一次考驗，我地係事前就知道要點做<br />\n每次都係靠我地團結先可以贏<br />\n回帶番去2019年頭，又有邊個諗過可以阻止到逃犯條例？<br />\n我地依家係經歷緊其他民主國家都經歷過既黑暗時期<br />\n近近地台灣都捱左幾十年先捱到今日<br />\n人地捱得過，唔通我地香港人就捱唔過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以團結起黎，我地係因為鐘意呢個地方先會走出黎，唔係為左要移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然如果真係出晒樣有危險既手足除外<br />\n同埋不如唔好再咁高調去批鬥同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算真係天滅左中共，我地都一樣要團結先可以贏到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢翻說話想講好耐，今日唔講唔知仲有冇機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔岩聽，今日大家都睇左好多唔開心既野<br />\n都可以當睇下卡通片，俾自己輕鬆幾分鐘<br />\n之後先再屌柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0383702407d4ffc6596cc1e119565f3f8867bd4","tid":2089370,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2357c018372f5208cd33cc24d2c4853f3a0ecf","tid":2089370,"uid":65457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"岩岩先share完張 我地真係好撚鐘意香港<br />\n希望太家唔好轉個頭就執行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1b119cfef933951f1950223a10ba862e86ce69","tid":2089370,"uid":65457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af85c1c8a85b621875333228c7997b833fa9c02","tid":2089370,"uid":65457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}